---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Beacon Design System — Graham Holt" description="A token-based design system unifying product experience across web, mobile, and marketing surfaces.">
  <div class="project">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <a href="/work" class="back">&larr; All Work</a>
        <div class="hero-meta">
          <span class="label">Design Systems</span>
          <span class="year">2025</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Beacon<br />Design System</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">
          Unifying product experience across web, mobile, and marketing —
          a token-first component library built for teams that move fast.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-tags">
          {['React', 'TypeScript', 'Figma', 'Storybook', 'CSS Tokens'].map(t => (
            <span class="tag">{t}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Cover -->
    <section class="cover-section container">
      <div class="cover-placeholder">
        <span class="cover-label">Beacon / Component Library</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <section class="stats container">
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">34</span>
        <span class="stat-desc">Components shipped</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">3</span>
        <span class="stat-desc">Surfaces unified</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">~90%</span>
        <span class="stat-desc">UI pattern coverage</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">1 day</span>
        <span class="stat-desc">Brand refresh turnaround</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="content container">

      <section class="block">
        <h2 class="block-title">Problem</h2>
        <p>
          The product had grown quickly across multiple teams. Buttons had four different
          border-radius values. The typescale was defined differently in Figma, the web
          codebase, and the mobile codebase. Designers and engineers spent significant
          time in every sprint re-solving the same layout, colour, and interaction problems.
        </p>
        <p>
          There was no shared language — decisions made on one surface didn't propagate
          anywhere else.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="block">
        <h2 class="block-title">Approach</h2>
        <p>
          I started by auditing every component in production, cataloguing what existed
          and where the divergence points were. From there I established a token layer —
          semantic colour, spacing, radius, and type scale — with dark and light themes
          built in from day one.
        </p>
        <div class="token-grid">
          <div class="token-group">
            <p class="token-group-label">Color</p>
            <div class="swatches">
              <div class="swatch" style="background:#c8ff57" title="Accent"></div>
              <div class="swatch" style="background:#e8e8e8" title="Text"></div>
              <div class="swatch" style="background:#888" title="Muted"></div>
              <div class="swatch" style="background:#1a1a1a" title="Surface"></div>
              <div class="swatch" style="background:#2e2e2e" title="Border"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="token-group">
            <p class="token-group-label">Radius</p>
            <div class="radius-row">
              <div class="radius-demo" style="border-radius:4px">sm</div>
              <div class="radius-demo" style="border-radius:8px">md</div>
              <div class="radius-demo" style="border-radius:12px">lg</div>
              <div class="radius-demo" style="border-radius:9999px">full</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>
          Components were built in React with TypeScript and consumed as a package across
          all surfaces. Each shipped with strict prop types, WCAG AA colour contrast, and
          a Storybook story covering every meaningful variant and state.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="block">
        <h2 class="block-title">Outcome</h2>
        <p>
          The system launched with 34 components covering ~90% of recurring UI patterns.
          Designer-to-developer handoff time dropped noticeably within the first quarter.
          New surfaces could be scaffolded from Beacon primitives without inheriting
          existing inconsistencies.
        </p>
        <p>
          The token architecture made a brand refresh the following year a tractable
          one-day task rather than a multi-sprint effort.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>

    <!-- Footer nav -->
    <div class="project-footer container">
      <a href="/work" class="back">&larr; All Work</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .project {
    padding-bottom: var(--space-24);
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    padding-top: var(--space-12);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-16);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .back {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }
  .back:hover { color: var(--color-text); }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .label {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .year {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-4xl), 8vw, 6rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 56ch;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .hero-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .tag {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-3);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Cover */
  .cover-section {
    padding-top: var(--space-12);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .cover-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 7;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .cover-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Stats */
  .stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--color-border);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .stat {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-6);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .stat-desc {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Content blocks */
  .content {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .block {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .block-title {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .block p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  /* Token demo */
  .token-grid {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-8);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    margin: var(--space-6) 0;
  }

  .token-group-label {
    font-size: var(--text-xs) !important;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3) !important;
  }

  .swatches {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .swatch {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }

  .radius-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .radius-demo {
    width: 40px;
    height: 28px;
    background: var(--color-surface-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Footer nav */
  .project-footer {
    padding-top: var(--space-12);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .stats {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
